佛仅 5 公里，这一发现有哪些重要意义？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "7 月 10 日，四川乐山，欧先生在餐厅用餐，无意间看到院子里的几个坑凹有些奇特。他仔细观察后发现，这很有可能是恐龙足迹。7 月 16 日，经专家团队考察研究，确定了这是白垩纪早期雷龙足迹，该足迹点距乐山大佛仅 5 公里。有意思的是，这是目前世界上唯一一个在餐厅发现的恐龙足迹。这次发现为该地区白垩纪早期的古环境、古生态增加了新的信息，也为日后在乐山地区找到更多的恐龙记录打下坚实基础。封面新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-6fd031096fc716ad532f8ebf4f518f97_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "266 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/543758718"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpqSzhamh+MdaEAMaCDgzMTE3ODc1IPuTzpYGMBQ4uQFACHIJNTQzNzU4NzE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1658055737.0186727", "card_id": "Q_543786293", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 58}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "警方通报「炫富网红疑用警用飞机拍段子」，称拍摄视频所用直升机为民用直升机，具体情况如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "炫富网红疑用警用飞机拍段子 警方通报"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-afdf706604bdd76e7e835076cc087f7a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "179 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/543786293"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpqSzhamh+MdaEAMaCDgzMTIzOTI5IOGMz5YGMAY4sQFACXIJNTQzNzg2MjkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1658055737.019125", "card_id": "Q_31682686", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 103}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《喜剧之王》中当周星驰说完「我养你啊」之后，柳飘飘在计程车上为什么会哭？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "你上次说养我是不是真的"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-21fcc495380370d4869730f165c7e63f_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "141 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "http